  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/6b5d7c87a99dbcee4327e3d52eab79db.avif?t=1744479197\" width=619 height=65 /></span>       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/fc29b9bf3d1bbc3baca63bf893e0da09.poster.avif?t=1744479197\" width=540 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/fc29b9bf3d1bbc3baca63bf893e0da09.webm?t=1744479197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/fc29b9bf3d1bbc3baca63bf893e0da09.mp4?t=1744479197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Necromorphosis</strong>, the undead roam in an endless conquest to claim the throne of skulls and reforge the law of skulls and bones. <strong>You are a Skeleton,</strong> risen from your grave once more to challenge this never-ending civil war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose your bones carefully,</strong> as you grow in power, feeding on the souls of the fallen. Here, only the strongest can survive, but even if you fall, heaven is not for you! Rise again, <strong>Skeleton</strong> and become the Bullet Hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/b9f34bf28f81a3529514b118c188f06f.avif?t=1744479197\" width=619 height=65 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Shape your Skeleton:</strong> Choose from weapons, arms, legs, skulls and assorted instruments of pain to craft the ultimate skeletal body.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Seek the Swarm:</strong> Endless hordes of nightmarish foes will challenge your claim, so stand your ground and take their strength for your own.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Search this Soil:</strong> Traverse through diverse maps to discover unique treasure, enemies, rulers, traps, secrets and even friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Seize their Supremacy: </strong>Defeat the merciless rulers who will test your skill and fortune, if you can prove yourself worthy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Survive and Survive:</strong> Even in death you find no rest, so rise again Skeleton, and see if your luck will last longer this time.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/8fbb85d05f90e90341070651a26d1033.avif?t=1744479197\" width=619 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/da60e9fbcae3241f40c9e54e19e6c375.poster.avif?t=1744479197\" width=540 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/da60e9fbcae3241f40c9e54e19e6c375.webm?t=1744479197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/da60e9fbcae3241f40c9e54e19e6c375.mp4?t=1744479197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
